PhantomPulse — a white-label SaaS platform (GoHighLevel-style)

PhantomPulse (Platform)
└── Agency (white-label customer)
    ├── Agency Owner / Admin
    └── SubAccount (client business)
        ├── Account Admin
        ├── Manager
        └── User

        What's done:

Entity hierarchy — Agency → SubAccount → User → Role → Permission
RBAC — Role, Permission, RolePermission with system roles seeded via SystemRoleType
Multi-tenancy — BaseEntity.TenantId drives EF global query filters, Platform scope bypasses
Auth plumbing — ITenantContext, TenantMiddleware, ICurrentUser, RefreshToken